{"type": "article", "id": 4619, "title": "Nike  Kobe 9 Elite 系列「What The」篮球鞋", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-23T07:58:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233408sU7CDvNy8bdEGiZm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tNike 日前公布了 Kobe 9 Elite 鞋款最新的「What The」配色作品，其延续了 Kobe 9 Elite 篮球鞋一贯的高筒状设计，赋予了全新的小清新风格配色，在左右脚采用了不同颜色的Flyknit 鞋面，形成了双脚的鲜明对比，透出一丝俏皮的味道。而在鞋舌内侧则呼应了 Kobe 9 Elite 典型的混搭主题，汇集了很多与 Kobe Bryant 相关的标签设计。这款鞋将于 1 月 10 日 8 时登陆 Nike.com，定价 225 美元（约合人民币 1399 元），<a href=\"http://www.nike.com/us/en_us/launch/c/2015-01/kobe-9-elite-what-the\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里关注</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233405AGC548YhWontFEfU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052334065WpkSlagcyYeNZDU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233406YDjvchJG56wfXaUK.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233407k018D9B7ds6EoIyv.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.884375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233407ChSc0qrLptsROXP9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}